extends ../../_layout/default.pug

block canonical
  link(rel='canonical' href='https://coreui.io/bootstrap/docs/components/chip/')

block breadcrumb
  +breadcrumb(
    [
      { href: '#', label: 'Home'},
      { label: 'Components'},
      { label: 'Notifications'},
      'Chip'
    ]
  )

block view
  +docs-components('https://coreui.io/bootstrap/docs/components/chip/')
  .row
    .col-lg-12
      .card.mb-4
        .card-header
          strong Chip
          span.small.ms-1 Basic and outline
        .card-body
          p.text-body-secondary.small
            | Chips are compact UI elements for labels, filters, and quick selections. Below are simple examples and outline variants based on the CoreUI component API.
          +example('https://coreui.io/bootstrap/docs/components/chip/#basic-chips')
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2
              span.chip Basic chip
              span.chip Frontend
              span.chip Design system
              span.chip Documentation
          p.text-body-secondary.small
            | Add 
            code .chip-outline
            |  to create a lighter, bordered appearance.
          +example('https://coreui.io/bootstrap/docs/components/chip/#outline-chips')
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2
              span.chip.chip-outline Outline chip
              span.chip.chip-outline Product
              span.chip.chip-outline Marketing
              span.chip.chip-outline Analytics
      .card.mb-4
        .card-header
          strong Chip
          span.small.ms-1 With icons and avatars
        .card-body
          p.text-body-secondary.small
            | Chips can include icons, user avatars, or avatar components to make tags easier to scan.
          +example('https://coreui.io/bootstrap/docs/components/chip/#chips-with-icons')
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2
              span.chip
                span.chip-icon
                  svg(width='16' height='16' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 16 16' aria-hidden='true')
                    path(d='M8 1a3 3 0 1 1 0 6 3 3 0 0 1 0-6Zm-5 12s0-3 5-3 5 3 5 3v1H3v-1Z')
                |  Team member
              span.chip
                span.chip-icon
                  svg(width='16' height='16' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 16 16' aria-hidden='true')
                    path(d='M2 2h12v2H2V2Zm0 5h8v2H2V7Zm0 5h12v2H2v-2Z')
                |  Backlog item
          +example('https://coreui.io/bootstrap/docs/components/chip/#chips-with-avatars')
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2
              span.chip
                img.chip-img(src='assets/img/avatars/1.jpg' width='16' height='16' alt='')
                |  Olivia Martin
              span.chip
                img.chip-img(src='assets/img/avatars/4.jpg' width='16' height='16' alt='')
                |  Ethan Carter
              span.chip
                span.avatar.avatar-sm.bg-primary.text-white A
                |  Account manager
              span.chip
                span.avatar.avatar-sm.bg-success.text-white Q
                |  QA owner
    .col-lg-12
      .card.mb-4
        .card-header
          strong Chip
          span.small.ms-1 Variants and sizes
        .card-body
          p.text-body-secondary.small
            | Variant classes make chips useful for filters and status states, and size modifiers help match denser or more spacious layouts.
          +example('https://coreui.io/bootstrap/docs/components/chip/#variants')
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2.mb-3
              span.chip.chip-primary.chip-clickable(tabindex='0') Product
              span.chip.chip-primary.active(tabindex='0') Active product
              span.chip.chip-success.chip-clickable(tabindex='0') Published
              span.chip.chip-success.active(tabindex='0') Live
              span.chip.chip-warning.chip-clickable(tabindex='0') Review
              span.chip.chip-danger.active(tabindex='0') Blocked
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2
              span.chip.chip-sm Small chip
              span.chip Default chip
              span.chip.chip-lg Large chip
              span.chip.chip-outline.chip-primary.chip-clickable(tabindex='0') Outline primary
      .card.mb-4
        .card-header
          strong Chip
          span.small.ms-1 Interactive examples
        .card-body
          p.text-body-secondary.small
            | The JavaScript plugin supports selectable and removable chips using 
            code data-coreui-chip
            |  attributes.
          +example('https://coreui.io/bootstrap/docs/components/chip/#data-attributes')
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2.mb-3
              span.chip(data-coreui-chip data-coreui-selectable='true') Selectable
              span.chip(data-coreui-chip data-coreui-selectable='true' data-coreui-selected='true') Selected
              span.chip(data-coreui-chip data-coreui-removable='true') Removable
              span.chip.disabled(data-coreui-chip) Disabled
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2
              span.chip.chip-lg
                | Team Alpha
                button.chip-remove(type='button' aria-label='Remove')
                  svg(width='16' height='16' viewBox='0 0 16 16' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' aria-hidden='true')
                    line(x1='4' y1='4' x2='12' y2='12')
                    line(x1='12' y1='4' x2='4' y2='12')
              span.chip.chip-outline.chip-info(data-coreui-chip data-coreui-selectable='true') Filter: Priority
              span.chip.chip-outline.chip-success(data-coreui-chip data-coreui-selectable='true' data-coreui-selected='true') Filter: Ready
